Comment: This game represents one my best games here at gameknot to date.  It seemed that I was able to see the whole board and generally speaking, played well tactically.  As I write this annotation, I have not utilized computer analysis as I wanted only my thoughts in my brain.  After I complete this annotation, I plan to run this through the computer analysis.  All comments and criticisms are welcome and appreciated.
